data.description: This duplex is located in the University Village subdivision.  Close to Texas A&M Central Texas, the Killeen Airport and easy access to Austin, Fort Cavazos and I14.  One unit is a 3 bed - 3 bath and the other unit is a 2 bed - 2 bath.  The exterior has rock accents and an extended patio off the back.  The interior offers wood laminate flooring throughout, black appliances, ceiling fan in living room and master bedroom.
